<br>
<br>

Appointments: <%= @performance_data['appointments_count'] %>
<br>
Treatment notes created: <%= @performance_data['treatment_notes_count'] %>
<br>
Letters created: <%= @performance_data['letters_count'] %>
<br>
Occupancy: <%= ((@performance_data['appointments_count'] / @performance_data['max_appointments'].to_f) * 100).round(2) %>%
<br>
Cancellation: <%= @performance_data['cancelleds_count'] %>
<br>
Invoice total: <%= format_money_amount @performance_data['invoiced_amount'] %>
<br>
Invoice total ex tax: <%= format_money_amount @performance_data['invoiced_amount_ex_tax'] %>
<br>
Average invoice: <%= format_money_amount (@performance_data['invoiced_amount'].to_f / @performance_data['appointments_count'].to_f).to_s %>
<br>
PVA(*): <%= @performance_data['appointments_count'].to_i.zero? ? 0 : (@performance_data['appointments_count'].to_f / @performance_data['patients_count'].to_f).round(1) %>
<br>
Availability duration: <%= (@performance_data['availability_duration'].to_f / 3600).round(2) %> hrs
<br>
Appointment duration: <%= (@performance_data['appointments_duration'].to_f / 3600).round(2) %> hrs
<br>
Travel distance: <%= (@performance_data['travel_distance'].to_f / 1000).round(2) %> km
<br>
Travel duration: <%= (@performance_data['travel_duration'].to_f / 3600).round(2) %> hrs
<br>
Vacant time: <%= (@performance_data['vacant_duration'].to_f / 3600).round(2) %> hrs
<br>
<br>
<small>
